    <h3>General Responsibilities</h3>

    <p>Our positions include general stagehands, semi-skilled and skilled technicians,
    theatrical staging and lighting, audio/visual, and other related work. Employees are expected to use professional expertise,
    discretion, and judgment in completing a wide range of assignments.
    Under general supervision, employees may be required to work independently within established parameters.
    Employees must ensure that all safety regulations and work rules are followed at all times. </p>
<br>
    <h3>Road Crew</h3>

    <p>We offer opportunities to travel out of state to provide staging support for various events.
    Travel time and work type are based upon client needs. Transportation, hotels, and per diem may be provided.
   </p>
  </div>

