  <div class="row table-box border border-secondary">
    <h3>Qualifications</h3>

    <ul class="list-indent">
      <li>Working knowledge of the tools, materials, methods, and practices used in the general installation, testing,
      operation, and removal of theatrical staging, sound, and lighting.</li>
      <li>Working knowledge of theatrical production terms, techniques, equipment parts and components.</li>
      <li>Working knowledge of occupational hazards and necessary safety procedures and equipment.</li>
      <li>Ability to communicate effectively, manage time efficiently, work under tight deadlines, and work as part of a team.</li>
      <li>Ability to lift 25 pounds repeatedly, 50-70 pounds frequently, and heavier on a limited basis.</li>
      <li>Ability to bend, twist, stoop, climb ladders, work from heights and perform other manual labor tasks.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

